Package: SamplingDesignTools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Dealing with Complex Sampling Designs
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Ning Yilin
Maintainer: Ning Yilin <ningyilinnyl@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Description: Provides functions for working with various study designs in
    epidemiological research, specifically to draw (matched) case-control samples, 
    to draw and analyse (more) extreme case-control samples, to compute 
    Kaplan-Meier type weights for analysis and partial reuse of nested case-control 
    (NCC) data, and to draw counter-matched NCC samples.
